{\an7}宇宙历年法
The cosmic calendar

834
01:01:54,810 --> 01:01:59,540
{\an7}把宇宙的历史压缩到一本365天日历
compresses the local history of the universe into a single year.

835
01:01:59,560 --> 01:02:02,100
{\an7}从1月1日宇宙诞生算起
If the universe began on January 1st,

836
01:02:02,120 --> 01:02:05,900
{\an7}我们的银河系要到5月才出现
it was not until May that the Milky Way formed.

837
01:02:04,870 --> 01:02:07,720
俗话说酒后吐真言
Drinking is not good for secrets.

838
01:02:07,740 --> 01:02:13,160
当儿子 儿媳还有那个名字听着像下雨的
And after the death of his son, daughter-in-law, and granddaughter-to-be,

839
01:02:13,180 --> 01:02:15,880
未来孙女艾雨莎全都去世后
Alyssa, who sounds like rain,

840
01:02:15,900 --> 01:02:19,210
阿尔比·克兰兹就拼命喝酒
Albie Krantz drank a great deal.

841
01:02:18,530 --> 01:02:22,430
{\an7}人类全部的历史
Everything humans have ever done occurred in that bright speck

842
01:02:22,450 --> 01:02:26,590
{\an7}都在这本日历的最后一天
at the lower right of the cosmic calendar.

843
01:02:25,370 --> 01:02:31,960
我打赌 从阁楼往外看 能看到西福商场
I'll bet you could see way past the Westford Mall from the cupola.

844
01:02:31,980 --> 01:02:37,360
整座小镇肯定也能看得一清二楚
You gotta be able to see the whole town from up there, I bet.

845
01:02:37,380 --> 01:02:43,710
要真上去了 你看见的可不只是风景
If you went up there, you might see a lot more than you wanted.

846
01:02:43,730 --> 01:02:47,110
小查 这门紧锁是有原因的
That's why it's locked, Chucko.

847
01:02:45,990 --> 01:02:49,370
{\an7}日历里每个月代表12.5亿年
Every month is one and a quarter billion years long.

848
01:02:49,390 --> 01:02:52,910
{\an7}每一天代表4000万年
Each day represents 40 million years.

849
01:02:52,170 --> 01:02:55,210
他想问清楚
He wanted to ask what Grandpa meant.

850
01:02:55,350 --> 01:02:59,160
尽管他才10岁
But the adult part of him, not there in person, no, not at 10,

851
01:02:59,180 --> 01:03:04,070
可脑子里的成熟声音冒出来
but something that had begun to speak on rare occasions,

852
01:03:04,090 --> 01:03:11,860
告诉他别吭声 安静地等着
told him to be quiet. Be quiet and wait.

853
01:03:10,800 --> 01:03:16,220
{\an7}人类的全部历史就像我手掌那么大
But all of human history would occupy an area the size of my hand.

854
01:03:16,240 --> 01:03:21,290
{\an7}现在让我们回到太古时代...
We're just beginning to trace the long and tortuous path which began with the primeval...

